<task>
<statement>
<p>
 <m>y(0)=0</m>,
         <m>\dfdxat{y}{x}{0}</m>  does not exist,
         <m> \geneval{\dfdx{y}{x}}{x\neq0}\gt0</m>,
         <m>  \dfdxn{y}{x}{2}\gt0</m>, for <m>x\lt0</m>
         <m> \dfdxn{y}{x}{2}\lt0</m>, for <m>x\gt0</m>
       </p>
