<statement>
<p>
 <m>y\gt0</m> for all <m>x</m>,
         <m>y(0)=1</m>,
         <m>\dfdx{y}{x}\gt0</m> for all <m>x</m>,
         <m>\dfdxn{y}{x}{2}\gt0</m> for all <m>x</m>.
       </p>
